quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Asikuvulelanga1 isifuba sakho na (Muhammad)
  94,2,Sakothulela umthwalo wakho
  94,3,Obukusinda umqolo
  94,4,Saza Saphakamisa ibakala lakho
  94,5,Inene kubo bonke ubunzima kukho ukukhululeka
  94,6,"Kanti, inene kubo bonke ubunzima kukho ukukhululeka"
  94,7,Ngoko ke wakugqiba (imisebenzi yakho yosuku) zinikele kunqulo luka-Allâh
  94,8,Yaye beka iingcinga zakho zonke eNkosini yakho
  95,1,Ndifunga ngomkhiwane nangomnquma
  95,2,Nangentaba yeSinayi
  95,3,Nangesi sixeko sokhuseleko (saseMakkah)
  95,4,Inene umntu Samdala ngesona simo silungileyo
  95,5,Saphinda Samthobisela kowona mgangatho uphantsi
  95,6,"Ngaphandle\tkwabo\tbakholwayo\tbenze\timisebenzi yobulungisa. Okwabo iya kuba ngumvuzo ongeze usilele"
  95,7,Yintoni ke emva koku enibangela ukuba niyiphike inkolo
  95,8,AyingoAllâh na Oyena Mgwebi Unobuluko kubagwebi
  96,1,Funda! Egameni leNkosi yakho Eyadalayo
  96,2,Yadala umntu ngehlwili legazi
  96,3,Funda iNkosi yakho Inesisa
  96,4,Yona Yafundisa ukubhala ngosiba
  96,5,Yamfundisa umntu oko abengakwazi
  96,6,Kodwa inene umntu uyagabadela
  96,7,Kuba uzicingela ukuba akaxhomekekanga ntweni
  96,8,Inene eNkosini yakho kulapho kuza kubuyelwa khona
  96,9,Umbonile na lowo uthintela
  96,10,Umkhonzi xa ethandaza
  96,11,Ingaba umbona ekuso isiKhokelo kusini na
  96,12,Okanye uyalela (abantu) ukuba bahlonele (uAllâh)
  96,13,"Umbonile na ukuba uphika inkolo, afulathele"
  96,14,Akazi na ukuba uAllâh Uyambona
  96,15,Nakanye ukuba akayeki siya kumrhuqa ngenwele zebunzi lakhe
  96,16,(Ezo) nwele zebunzi lexoki
  96,17,Makabize koogxabakhe (bamncede) ke
  96,18,Thina Siya kubiza abagcini siHogo. (Baqubisane naye)
  96,19,"Nakanye! Ungamthobeli lowo, wena, qubuda, uzisondeze (kuAllâh)"
  97,1,Inene esi siTyhilelo Sasityhila ngoBusuku baMandla
  97,2,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba buyintoni na uBusuku baMandla
  97,3,UBusuku baMandla bungcono kuneenyanga eziliwaka
  97,4,"Ngabo kuhla iingelosi noMoya [oyiNgcwele (uJibrîl)] ngemvume ka-Allâh nemiyalelo yonke"
  97,5,(Ngobo busuku) kuba luxolo kude kube ngoms’obomvu
  98,1,Abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi nabanquli-zithixo babengekhe bayeke (ukuba ngabahedeni) de kwafika ubungqina obucacileyo kubo
  98,2,UMthunywa ovela kuAllâh ecengceleza iziBhalo eziNgcwele
  98,3,Apho kuzo kukho iiNcwadi ezilungileyo nezithe Tye
  98,4,Kananjalo aBantu beNcwadi babengezontlaba zahlukane de kwafika ubungqina obucacileyo
  98,5,"Ukanti babengayalelwanga nto yimbi ngaphandle kokukuba, banqule uAllâh, banyaniseke enkolweni yaKhe, banquleYena Yedwa, benze iSalâh (umthandazo), banikele ngeZakâh, oko ke yayiyeyona Nkolo ithe Tye"
  98,6,"Inene abo bangakholwayo phakathi kwaBantu beNcwadi nabanquli-zithixo baya kuba seMlilweni wesiHogo, ngonaphakade, bazezona zidalwa zibi"
  98,7,"Inene, ke bona abo bakholwayo, benza imisebenzi yobulungisa, bazezona zidalwa zilungileyo"
  98,8,"Umvuzo wabo oseNkosini yabo yiEdeni (uMyezo iPaladesi), ekumpompoza amanzi phantsi kwayo. Baya kuhlala apho kuyo ngonaphakade, uAllâh Uya kukholiseka ngabo nabo bakholiseke nguYe. Oko kokwabo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo"
  99,1,Xa umhlaba uNyikima ngokunyikima kwawo
  99,2,"Uze\tutyekezele\tngaphandle\twonke\tumthwalo\twawo (obungaphakathi kuwo)"
  99,3,"Abantu baya kuthi: “kwenzeka ntoni na ngawo?”"
  99,4,Ngaloo Mini uya kuchaza iindaba zawo
  99,5,Kuba iNkosi yakho Iya kuwutyhilela (okwenzekayo phezu kwawo)
  99,6,"Ngaloo Mini abantu baya kuza bengamaqela athe saa, beze kuboniswa izenzo zabo"
  99,7,"Nabani\tna\tlowo\tuthe\twenza\tisenzo\tesilungileyo esingangentlantsi, uya kusibona"
  99,8,"Nalowo uthe wenza isenzo esingcolileyo esingangentlantsi, uya kusibona"
  100,1,"Ndifunga ngamahashe agabadula, akhefuzele"
  100,2,Atakise iintlantsi zomlilo (ngamanqina awo)
  100,3,Ephumelelisa uhlaselo lwawo kwasekuseni
  100,4,Aqhumise uthuli luye kutsho emafini kusenjalo
  100,5,"Agqobhoze, aye phambili angene esazulwini (sotshaba)"
  100,6,Inene umntu (ongakholwayo) akanambulelo eNkosini yakhe (uAllâh)
  100,7,Yaye inene ulingqina lako oko (ngezenzo zakhe)
  100,8,Kwaye inene unobutyhuthu-tyhuthu ekuthandeni kwakhe ubutyebi